"Participants": "Kidney transplant recipients",
"Intervention": "Inhibition of BAFF system using a specific inhibitor",
"Outcome measures": "Incidence of acute rejection, chronic allograft damage, and graft survival",
"Equipment": "Real-time PCR, flow cytometry, and histopathological analysis",
"Steps": [
